The '''Sanche Ocean''' was a large body of [[Water/Legends|water]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Gandle Ott]]. [[Montrol City]] was located on its shoreline, where [[Navy/Legends|naval]] docks and harbors supported those that plied their trade on the [[Ocean/Legends|ocean]].

